proposal:
Hello everyone, 

Hope you're all minting tokens as fresh as morning dew with TokenMint! 😊

We've been keeping an eye on your project and we must say, we're impressed. Your vision aligns with ours, and we believe we can add value to your community with our B2B tools.

Just like TokenMint, our tools are built to empower communities. We offer a range of B2B tools from DEX and Lottery to DAO and CrossChain, all designed to support the growth of communities like yours. 

Here's the kicker, our DEX and Lottery tools are revenue share tools, meaning that anyone from your community can deploy them. And the best part? You don't have to pay a dime upfront. 

We're not just a shop, we're a marketplace of B2B tools waiting for you to explore. So why not take a look and see how we can grow together? 

Check out our demos at https://t.me/onoutdemos. 

Remember, with our tools, you're not just playing, you're creating. Let's create something amazing together! 👋

(P.S. We promise we won't mint any tokens while you're away 😉)
